description:
- C O M P L E X

P R E S E N T S  :

Brunswick Pro Bowling (c) 505 Games

Region      : PAL                  Languages: English
Size        : 1 DVD                Genre    : Kinect
Platform    : XBOX 360              Date    : April, 2011

Release Info:

- Full support for Xbox 360 Kinect
- Brunswick Pro Bowling provides the most authentic bowling experience
on Next Gen featuring accurate ball and pin physics as well as detailed
oil patterns
- Compete on 6 highly detailed bowling environments, each with unique
characteristics
- Roll on 5 different gameplay settings including: Exhibition, Online,
League, Tournament, and the Spares Challenge
- Customize your bowler in authentic Brunswick gear like shirts,
shoes, and bowling balls
- Kid-friendly bumper bowling option makes it fun for all ages
